description:
RHS Chelsea Flower Show 2015




Secrets of the Great Pavilion

If you have been inspired to get out into your own garden, then take some top tips from the expert growers in the Great Pavilion at this year's RHS Chelsea Flower Show. Toby Buckland and Ann-Marie Powell meet the professionals, to hear the secrets of their success.




Original Air Date: 22-May-2015
